<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="ida77354bd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/99/433/tII/s214/d">Pub. L. 99–433, title II, § 214(d)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-01">Oct. 1, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1019">100 Stat. 1019</ref>, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/99/433/tII/s214/d">“<ref href="/us/usc/t10/s166">Section 166 of title 10</ref>, United States Code (as added by section 211 of this Act), shall take effect with budget proposals for fiscal year 1989.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
